ns.</p> </div> <div class=\"info-section\"> <h3>📐 Universal Textile Requirements (All 100 Designs)</h3> <div class=\"table-container\"> <table> <thead> <tr> <th>Specification</th> <th>Requirement</th> <th>Why It Matters</th> </tr> </thead> <tbody> <tr> <td><strong>Resolution</strong></td> <td>300 DPI minimum</td> <td>Prevents pixelation on large-format textile printing</td> </tr> <tr> <td><strong>Pixel Dimensions</strong></td> <td>15,000 × 18,000 pixels</td> <td>Exact size for 50×60 inch woven blanket</td> </tr> <tr> <td><strong>Edge-Safe Margin</strong></td> <td>0.5 inches on all sides</td> <td>Prevents critical design elements from being cut off in production trimming</td> </tr> <tr> <td><strong>Print Bleed Zone</strong></td> <td>0.25 inches beyond edges</td> <td>Allows for production trimming variations</td> </tr> <tr> <td><strong>Minimum Line Weight</strong></td> <td>3-5pt thickness</td> <td>Thinner lines get lost in woven fabric texture (typical 5-8mm pile height)</td> </tr> <tr> <td><strong>Minimum Detail Size</strong></td> <td>2-3mm elements</td> <td>Ultra-fine details are obscured by fabric weave</td> </tr> <tr> <td><strong>Color Mode</strong></td> <td>CMYK or rich RGB</td> <td>Compatible with textile dye sublimation/direct-to-fabric printing</td> </tr> <tr> <td><strong>Color Saturation</strong></td> <td>Boost 10-15% from screen</td> <td>Compensates for slight dulling on textile surface</td> </tr> <tr> <td><strong>Gradient Smoothness</strong></td> <td>15-20% shift per inch minimum</td> <td>Prevents visible banding on fabric printing</td> </tr> <tr> <td><strong>Viewing Distance</strong></td> <td>Optimized for 3-6 feet</td> <td>Typical blanket use/display distance</td> </tr> </tbody> </table> </div> </div> <div class=\"info-section\" style=\"margin-top: 30px;\"> <h3>🎯 Why Textile Optimization Matters</h3> <div style=\"background: var(--light); padding: 25px; border-radius: 12px;\"> <ul style=\"list-style-position: inside; line-height: 2.2;\"> <li><strong>Fabric Texture Visibility:</strong> Woven blankets have natural pile (5-8mm) that affects design appearance</li> <li><strong>Production Safety:</strong> Printful trims edges—designs need safe margins to avoid cropping</li> <li><strong>Color Accuracy:</strong> Textile dye sublimation has different color reproduction than screen display</li> <li><strong>Detail Preservation:</strong> Ultra-fine details disappear in fabric weave—designs must be scaled appropriately</li> <li><strong>Customer Satisfaction:</strong> Production-ready files = no rejected orders, no print quality complaints</li> <li><strong>Professional Quality:</strong> Premium $75-125 blankets demand premium print execution</li> </ul> </div> </div> <div class=\"info-section\" style=\"margin-top: 30px;\"> <h3>🎨 Category-Specific Textile Adaptations</h3> <div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; margin-top: 20px;\"> <div style=\"background: white; border: 2px solid var(--primary); border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px;\"> <h4 style=\"color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 10px;\">🐾 Pet Memorial</h4> <ul style=\"line-height: 1.8; font-size: 0.9rem;\"> <li>Photo integration: 300 DPI minimum</li> <li>Border safety: 0.5\" margin around pet photos</li> <li>Color richness: Boost saturation 10-15%</li> <li>Emotional details: Keep visible on fabric</li> </ul> </div> <div style=\"background: white; border: 2px solid var(--secondary); border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px;\"> <h4 style=\"color: var(--secondary); margin-bottom: 10px;\">📸 Personalized Photo</h4> <ul style=\"line-height: 1.8; font-size: 0.9rem;\"> <li>Multi-photo layouts: 0.5\" spacing between photos</li> <li>Text elements: Minimum 14pt font, 5pt stroke</li> <li>Collage spacing: Account for fabric texture</li> <li>Border designs: Safe margin compliance</li> </ul> </div> <div style=\"background: white; border: 2px solid var(--success); border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px;\"> <h4 style=\"color: var(--success); margin-bottom: 10px;\">🎨 Abstract Emotional</h4> <ul style=\"line-height: 1.8; font-size: 0.9rem;\"> <li>Pattern repeats: Seamless 24-30\" tiles</li> <li>Line weights: Bold 4-6pt for fabric visibility</li> <li>Centered designs: 5-10\" border space</li> <li>Gradients: Smooth transitions (no banding)</li> </ul> </div> <div style=\"background: white; border: 2px solid var(--warning); border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px;\"> <h4 style=\"color: var(--warning); margin-bottom: 10px;\">🎉 Milestone Celebration</h4> <ul style=\"line-height: 1.8; font-size: 0.9rem;\"> <li>Vibrant colors: Rich saturation for joy</li> <li>Timeline designs: Horizontal 50×60 orientation</li> <li>Date/text: Bold 18pt+ fonts</li> <li>Celebratory elements: 6-8\" minimum size</li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> <div class=\"info-section\" style=\"margin-top: 30px;\"> <h3>🚀 Textile-Optimized Prompt Structure</h3> <div class=\"ai-prompt-box\" style=\"position: relative;\"> <div style=\"color: #10b981; margin-bottom: 15px; font-weight: 700;\">UPDATED PROMPT FORMAT (All Category 5 Designs):</div> **TEXTILE PRINTING SPECIFICATIONS FOR WOVEN BLANKET:** [Design description] DESIGN FOR TEXTILE: This artwork will be printed on a 50x60 inch woven blanket using dye sublimation or direct-to-fabric printing. Design must account for fabric texture and weave visibility. TECHNICAL REQUIREMENTS: - Resolution: 300 DPI minimum (15000 x 18000 pixels) - Color Mode: CMYK or rich RGB for textile dye sublimation - Edge-Safe Margin: 0.5-inch safety zone on all edges - Line Weights: [Design-specific, typically 3-6pt minimum] - Print Bleed: 0.25-inch bleed zone - Fabric Considerations: [Pattern repeats, viewing distance, etc.] - Gradient Handling: Smooth transitions to prevent fabric banding - Detail Sizing: Elements sized for visibility on woven texture [Original design description continues...] </div> <p style=\"margin-top: 15px; color: var(--text-light); font-style: italic;\"> 📁 Full textile-optimized prompts available in: <code>category5_ai_prompts_TEXTILE_OPTIMIZED.csv</code> </p> </div> <div class=\"info-section\" style=\"margin-top: 30px;\"> <h3>✅ Pre-Upload Verification Checklist</h3> <div style=\"background: var(--success); color: white; padding: 25px; border-radius: 12px;\"> <p style=\"font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 15px;\"><strong>Before uploading to Printful, verify:</strong></p> <div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 15px;\"> <div style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px;\"> <strong>✓ Resolution:</strong> 300 DPI minimum </div> <div style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px;\"> <strong>✓ Dimensions:</strong> 15,000 × 18,000 px </div> <div style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px;\"> <strong>✓ Edge Margin:</strong> 0.5\" safe zone </div> <div style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px;\"> <strong>✓ Line Weights:</strong> 3-5pt minimum </div> <div style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px;\"> <strong>✓ Colors:</strong> CMYK/rich RGB </div> <div style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px;\"> <strong>✓ Gradients:</strong> Smooth transitions </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class=\"info-section\" style=\"margin-top: 30px;\"> <h3>📖 Complete Textile Guide</h3> <p>For comprehensive textile printing specifications, troubleshooting, and category-specific guidance, reference:</p> <div style=\"background: var(--primary); color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; margin-top: 15px; text-align: center;\"> <div style=\"font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px;\">📄 TEXTILE_PRINTING_GUIDE.md</div> <p style=\"opacity: 0.9;\">Complete specifications, AI model recommendations, and design-specific textile notes</p> </div> </div> </div> TEXTILE_EOF echo \"Textile insert created\" View Textile insert created Exit Code: 0