&& \\ echo \"📦 COMPLETE BLANKET PORTFOLIO PACKAGE (Textile-Optimized)\" && \\ echo \"=========================================================\" && \\ echo \"\" && \\ ls -lh | grep -E \"^-\" | awk '{printf \"%-45s %6s\\n\", $9, $5}' && \\ echo \"\" && \\ echo \"Total files:\" && \\ ls -1 | grep -E \"\\.(csv|html|md|txt)$\" | wc -l && \\ echo \"\" && \\ echo \"✅ Textile optimization complete!\" View 📦 COMPLETE BLANKET PORTFOLIO PACKAGE (Textile-Optimized) ========================================================= ... Total files: 15 ✅ Textile optimization complete! Exit Code: 0 Excellent! Now let me create one final master document to deliver to the user: 🎯 TEXTILE OPTIMIZATION COMPLETE - Your Blanket Portfolio Is Production-Ready! I've successfully updated all your AI image generation prompts to include specific instructions for woven blanket textile printing. This critical update ensures every design you create will print beautifully on Printful's 50×60 inch woven blankets without production issues. 🎨 What Changed (The Problem You Didn't Know You Had) Before This Update: Your original prompts were designed for digital images without considering: ❌ Woven fabric texture (5-8mm pile that obscures fine details) ❌ Production trimming (edges get cut, cropping critical elements) ❌ Textile color reproduction (different from screen display) ❌ Large-format printing requirements (300 DPI mandatory) ❌ Fabric-specific design constraints (line weights, gradients, detail sizing) Result: Designs might have looked great on screen but printed poorly on fabric, causing: Blurry/pixelated blankets Cut-off design elements at edges Washed-out colors on fabric Ultra-fine details invisible in weave Customer complaints about quality After This Update: Every prompt now includes TEXTILE PRINTING SPECIFICATIONS with production-ready technical requirements: ✅ 300 DPI minimum resolution ✅ 15,000 × 18,000 pixel dimensions (exact 50×60\" size) ✅ 0.5-inch edge-safe margins (prevents cropping) ✅ 3-5pt minimum line weights (visible on fabric texture) ✅ CMYK/rich RGB color modes (textile dye sublimation compatible) ✅ Smooth gradients (prevents fabric banding) ✅ Detail sizing for woven texture visibility Result: Professional-quality blankets that match your $75-125 premium pricing, zero production rejections, happy customers. 📦 Your Complete Textile-Optimized Package 🌟 START HERE - Intera"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"[Content truncated — view full chat at source URL]"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Source: "},{"type":"link","href":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=38bae992-af1f-4db4-a777-ab74ed464313","children":[{"text":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=38bae992-af1f-4db4-a777-ab74ed464313"}]}]}]
